Sorry, it's not a publicly available page yet. :disappointed:

Here is more info:

1) This is a new portal.
2) There is nothing being loaded in the domain settings area for fonts or any other scripts.
3) The theme is not loading any fonts except what is set in the settings, which is Raleway.
4) Nothing else has been done here except adding this module with the payment integration. If I remove the payment piece, all of the console errors go away.

I also switched the page to use the core "Growth" theme and all of the same console errors remained. There has to be something tied to the payments script from the HubSpot Payments link.
gotcha. What exact payment module are you trying to integrate?
The payment field that is an option for module fields. I'm adding this field in a custom module. It's in a group that is a repeater as the module shows multiple payment links.
looks like a issue on HubSpots end :confused:
did you get in touch with the support team?
